#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/browser.rst:50
msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Settings --> Interface Customization` it is possible "
"to disable resources. If you, for instance, would not like to show Python"
" scripts in the browser, you can uncheck the :menuselection:`Browser --> "
"py` entry, and if you want to get rid of your home folder in the browser,"
" you can uncheck the :menuselection:`Browser --> special:Home` entry."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/browser.rst:57
